        "My morning routine: wake up, crack everything, assess the damage, proceed.",
        "The last time I sat cross-legged on the floor, I needed a search and rescue team.",
        "I bought a yoga mat. It's been rolled up in the closet for two years. We're working on trust.",
        "My knee sounds like a stapler every time I walk downstairs.",
        "I set a personal record today: I stood up on the first try.",
        "My joints creak so much, I sound like an old pirate ship in a storm.",
