        "My neck cracks so loud in meetings, people think I'm disagreeing aggressively.",
        "I Googled 'why do my joints crack' and the first result said 'because you're old.'",
        "I bought a standing desk to help my back. Now my feet hurt too.",
        "My body makes a full percussion kit sound when I do a Turkish get-up.",
