        "I tried pigeon pose. The pigeon community sent a cease and desist.",
        "My morning mobility takes 30 minutes. My actual workout takes 20. Priorities.",
        "I have the flexibility of a LEGO figure. The original kind. Not the bendy ones.",
        "I walked into a CrossFit gym and my joints immediately went on strike.",
        "My hip makes a clicking sound that my kids use as a metronome.",
        "I used to be able to sit Indian-style. Now I sit 'call-the-ambulance style.'",
        "My shoulder pops so loud during push-ups that people think I'm clapping.",
        "I started stretching and heard a noise. Turns out that was my self-esteem cracking.",
        "My glutes are so inactive, they haven't clocked in since 2019.",
        "I tried a wall sit. The wall won.",
        "My thoracic spine has the mobility of a parking meter.",
        "I hung from a bar at the playground. Five kids gathered to watch the struggle.",
        "My right shoulder clicks, my left shoulder crunches, and my ego just whimpers.",
        "I can hear my own knee cap from inside my head. That can't be normal.",
        "I take glucosamine, fish oil, turmeric, and collagen. My joints are still rude.",
        "I tried a backbend once. My spine said, 'This is a forward-only operation.'",
        "My recovery day looks exactly like my workout day, but horizontal.",
        "I told my kids I used to be athletic. They didn't even look up from their phones.",
        "My deep squat is everyone else's shallow curtsy.",
        "I went to a chiropractor and he cracked things I didn't even know could crack.",
        "My body is a temple. An ancient one. With poor structural integrity.",
        "I stretched my hamstring and it twanged like a banjo string.",
        "My trainer said 'move with intention.' My intention was to not collapse.",
        "My idea of active recovery is walking to the fridge and back without groaning.",
        "I tried hanging from a doorframe pull-up bar. The bar held. My dignity didn't.",
